HIV cell clustering, using integrated expression from Mesmer, normalize each cell by total

Candace Liu

January 19, 2022

  • For each cell, divide each marker by total (each cell sums to 1)
  • z-score cap=3 for hierarchical clustering
  • k=20 (cell metaclusters)
